[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    283[0m:[38;5;10m[49m       ...
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    284[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    285[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - In `screen_output`, when hallucination is caught:
