[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    289[0m:[38;5;10m[49m       _increment_session_counter(session_id, "hallucination_count")
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    290[0m:[38;5;10m[49m       ...
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    291[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    292[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - In `_handle_in_scope_message`, when an out-of-scope handoff template is delivered:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    293[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   ```python
