[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    423[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    424[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ### N3. The disposition strings emitted from chat replies (`continued`, `no_information_offered`, `clarification_requested`, `handoff_offered`) don't reconcile with the four `final_disposition` branches in the audit record (`contained`, `crisis_routed`, `escalated`, `abandoned`, `other`)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    425[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    426[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Files / sections:**
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    427[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - `_build_chat_reply` (called from multiple sites):
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    428[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   - `disposition: "continued"` (after PHI redirect or injection refusal)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    429[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   - `disposition: "crisis_routed"` (after crisis response)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    430[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   - `disposition: "clarification_requested"` (low-confidence classifier)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    431[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   - `disposition: "handoff_offered"` (out-of-scope category)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    432[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   - `disposition: "contained"` (in-scope answered)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    433[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   - `disposition: "no_information_offered"` (no relevant chunks)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    434[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - `close_conversation_and_archive`:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    435[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   ```python
