[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    588[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - `_handle_screening_action` for `phi_redirect` calls `_flag_turn_for_redaction(...)` and then proceeds.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    589[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - `_redact_turn_for_audit` (called at conversation close) runs `_redact_pii_for_logging` over every turn's text regardless of whether the turn was flagged.
